name: Rust-Oleum V2100 Rust Preventative Enamels
meta_description: Rust-Oleum V2100 Rust Preventative Enamels Are The Ideal Spray Paint For Industrial Applications.
description: Rust-Oleum V2100 Rust Preventative Enamels Are The Ideal Spray Paint For Industrial Applications.
short_description: Rust-Oleum V2100 Rust Preventative Enamels provide maximum corrosion protection and long lasting durability. High paint solids allow for excellent coverage in one coat. Dries fast (20 minutes to touch) and is 20% faster than other brands. Tough, professional finish provides superior resistance to chipping, cracking and peeling. Superior gloss retention provides a lasting effect. Can be used on surfaces that reach temperatures of up to 200°F. Comes in a 20 oz. aerosol can. Available in a wide variety of colors.

Dries fast (20 minutes to touch) and is 20% faster than other brands. Tough, professional finish provides superior resistance to chipping, cracking and peeling. Superior gloss retention provides a lasting effect. Can be used on surfaces that reach temperatures of up to 200°F. Comes in a 20 oz. aerosol can. Available in a wide variety of colors.

name: ALL - 4 SPRAY LUBRICANT 12OZ (CRC 03005) AERVOE 7340
description: Stop squeaks, ensure smooth operation and prevent rust with Rust-Oleum Multi-Purpose Lubricant. This versatile spray can loosen rusted parts, drive out moisture and provide ongoing lubrication. One can does it all.
short_description:
Leaves behind a lubricating film that protects against rust and corrosion
  • Resists water wash-off—provides lasting protection
  • Specifically designed for the demands of industrial settings
  • Great for metal parts that are rusted or exposed to moisture—hinges, bolts, etc.
  • Convenient, extra-large can; sprays from any angle, even upside down
summary:
Available Sizes
16 oz. Spray

name: SILICONE LUBE AERVOE 8034
description: Get food-safe lubrication, protection and waterproofing with Rust-Oleum Food Grade Silicone. This proven formula is highly effective at eliminating squeaks and reducing friction in industrial equipment.
short_description:
NSF-approved1; safe for settings that include incidental food contact
  • Non-staining; repels water; works on rubber, plastic, wood, metal and painted surfaces
  • Effective as a lubricant, release agent, protective coating or anti-rust film
  • Ideal for conveyors, o-rings, tracks, gaskets/seals, etc. in food-processing facilities
  • Convenient, extra-large can
summary:
Available Sizes
11 oz. Spray

description: Provide long-lasting color and protection to outdoor machinery with Rust-Oleum High Performance V2100 System Farm Equipment Spray. This high-gloss industrial enamel comes in a full range of original-equipment colors and produces a tough, durable finish.
short_description:
Tough, professional finish—superior resistance to chipping, cracking and peeling
  • High-output tip covers 50% faster; dries in only 20 minutes to touch
  • Withstands heat to 200° F • Extra-wide comfort nozzle prevents finger fatigue and sprays from any angle, even upside down
  • Meets USDA requirements for incidental food contact; VOC-compliant nationwide

name: BLACK SATIN PAINT NON-RUST
description: New Rust-Oleum® Universal® is specifically formulated to work on diverse surfaces including wood, plastic, metal, wood, concrete and even vinyl. The Rust-Oleum® Universal® advanced spray system can spray from any angle — even upside down.
short_description:
For use on interior / exterior environments
  • One Universal coating for diverse substrates
  • Ultimate flexibility for extreme applications
  • Maximum adhesion for demanding substrates
  • Fast, efficient coverage
  • Fade and chip resistant
  • Rust preventative
  • 2008 HANDY Innovation Award Winner
  • AVAILABLE SIZES
